      "date": "2011-07-19 15:45:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/52f423de-b21d-11e0-b33f-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
